WEBVTT

00:10:29.527 --> 00:10:31.841
the similarities were staggering.

00:10:33.931 --> 00:10:36.119
Almost every single person

00:10:36.828 --> 00:10:40.667
first asked for good health
for themselves and their families.

00:10:42.001 --> 00:10:43.378
Almost universally,

00:10:44.212 --> 00:10:45.686
they next asked for happiness

00:10:46.829 --> 00:10:47.980
and then love,

00:10:49.439 --> 00:10:50.615
in that order:

00:10:51.824 --> 00:10:53.579
health, happiness, love.

00:10:55.585 --> 00:10:58.512
Sometimes they asked for a specific
health issue to be fixed,

00:10:58.536 --> 00:11:01.858
but more often than not, they just
asked for good health in general.